DOC.HEADLINE: PACIFIC WATCH : AUSTRALIA
DOC.TEXT: Jobless Rate Revised Downward : The Bureau of Statistics updated its employment data for the past six months , dropping the January jobless rate to 10.5 % from a previously reported 10.6 % . The revised figure is the lowest unemployment_rate since April , 1992 . " There is a strong possibility of a sub-10 % unemployment_rate by the end of 1994 , " the bureau said .
